headline: Trane Technologies (TT) Expands Liquid Cooling Solutions for AI Data Centers
summary: Trane Technologies plc (NYSE:TT) is one of the 11 best European stocks to invest in. On June 10, Trane announced the expansion of its liquid cooling capabilities for data centers. As part of the initiative, the company introduced new scalable Coolant Distribution Unit (CDU) solutions with capacities ranging from 2.5 megawatts (MW) to 10 MW. […]
